load logistic factor analysis results

LF <- readRDS( "./data/preprocessed/lf5.rds")
#this runs the logistic regression
lreg_dich <- function(y, X){
  
  b <- glm2(cbind(y, 2-y) ~ -1 + X, family="binomial")$coef
  
  return(b)
  
}
#modified from gcat
fit_glm_dich <- function(..., LF, trait){
  snp <- c(...)
  snp <- as.numeric((snp==1) | (snp==2))
  ind <- !is.na(snp) #logical index vector
  snp_no_na <- snp[ind]
  LF_no_na <- LF[ind,]
  p0 <- rep(NA, length(snp))
  p1 <- rep(NA, length(snp))
  trait_no_na <- trait[ind]
  b0 <- lreg_dich(snp_no_na, LF_no_na) #coefficients from logreg 
  b1 <- lreg_dich(snp_no_na, cbind(LF_no_na, trait_no_na))
  est0 <- .Call("mv", LF_no_na, b0)
  est1 <- .Call("mv", cbind(LF_no_na, trait_no_na), b1)
  p0[ind] <- exp(est0)/(1+exp(est0))
  p1[ind] <- exp(est1)/(1+exp(est1))
  
  dataset <-
    tibble(snp=snp,
           p0 = p0,
           p1 = p1)
  
  stat <-
    dataset %>%
    summarize( #cross entropy (log likelihood)
      dev0 = -2 * sum(snp * log(p0) +
                        (1 - snp) * log(1 - p0),
                      na.rm = TRUE),
      dev1 = -2 * sum(snp * log(p1) +
                        (1 - snp) * log(1 - p1),
                      na.rm = TRUE),
      devdiff = dev0 - dev1,
      dev_logp = -log10(pchisq(devdiff,
                               1,
                               lower.tail = FALSE))
    ) %>% 
    mutate(num_nas = sum(!ind),
       num_zeros= sum(snp_no_na ==0),
           b=b1[length(b1)])
  
  return(list(dataset=dataset, stat=stat))
         
}

define functions

#this runs the logistic regression
lreg <- function(y, X){
  X <- rbind(X, X)
  y1 <- as.numeric((y==1) | (y==2))
  y2 <- as.numeric(y==2)
  y <- c(y1,y2)
  b <- glm2(cbind(y, 2-y) ~ -1 + X, family="binomial")$coef
  
  return(b)
  
}
#modified from gcat
fit_glm <- function(..., LF, trait){
  snp <- c(...)
  ind <- !is.na(snp) #logical index vector
  snp_no_na <- snp[ind]
  LF_no_na <- LF[ind,]
  p0 <- rep(NA, length(snp))
  p1 <- rep(NA, length(snp))
  trait_no_na <- trait[ind]
  b0 <- lreg(snp_no_na, LF_no_na) #coefficients from logreg 
  b1 <- lreg(snp_no_na, cbind(LF_no_na, trait_no_na))
  est0 <- .Call("mv", LF_no_na, b0)
  est1 <- .Call("mv", cbind(LF_no_na, trait_no_na), b1)
  p0[ind] <- exp(est0)/(1+exp(est0))
  p1[ind] <- exp(est1)/(1+exp(est1))
  
  dataset <-
    tibble(snp=snp,
           p0 = p0,
           p1 = p1)
  
  stat <-
    dataset %>%
    summarize(
      dev0 = -2 * sum(snp * log(p0) +
                        (2 - snp) * log(1 - p0),
                      na.rm = TRUE),
      dev1 = -2 * sum(snp * log(p1) +
                        (2 - snp) * log(1 - p1),
                      na.rm = TRUE),
      devdiff = dev0 - dev1,
      dev_logp = -log10(pchisq(devdiff,
                               1,
                               lower.tail = FALSE))
    ) %>% 
    mutate(num_nas = sum(!ind),
       num_zeros= sum(snp_no_na ==0),
           b=b1[length(b1)])
  
  return(list(dataset=dataset, stat=stat))
         
}
